{"tid":991420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自殺式兇習）重慶男當眾演講　大喊「罷免習近平」","createTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T14:25:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c576c9aebe6de9470bf7ef7c721375d9c6f03d4","tid":991420,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"中國重慶一名異議人士張吉林，在重慶江北區觀音橋廣場，打算公開發表演講「罷免中國國家主席習近平」的言論，遭到10多名當地警方，被以涉嫌尋釁滋事罪，刑事逮捕、拘留。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由亞洲電台》報導，中國異議人士張吉林，網名岳家槍，17日晚間在微信群組裡面發表「針砭中國時局的言論」。18日他又在微信群裡面預告，表明要到觀音橋廣場去發表演講，下午4點抵達後，正當他向群眾演講時，10多名警察立刻將他逮捕，上手銬押至一輛無牌小轎車離開，同時發出刑事拘留通知書。<br />\n<br />\n張吉林演講的錄音提到「我認為罷免習近平，已經水到渠成，中共是不會把我們怎麼樣的，不信你們就看，我在廣場上整天的演講，人聚得越來越多，我既然敢講，難道還不敢聽嗎，所以我相信我們觀音橋這個地方，是追求民主憲政，實現民主憲政的橋頭堡。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=489178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D489178&d=ah4jksLE9LN9r3P%2BgshA5W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e9a5d0a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D489178&h=3c6cb6a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=489178</a>"},{"pid":"4c221aaa03586688d9078c6b613a988e62942e01","tid":991420,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e50508b954ba2e0fb958da70dc226a173d7df71","tid":991420,"uid":212317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"RIP   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd03b2a15ef2e5987e1f48d016006312b2e